  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Project Engineer (CCTV,IDS,ACS)",
  "description": "<p><strong>What We Offer:</strong></p><ul><li>Health insurance & dental reimbursement</li><li>AWS + performance bonus</li><li>Friendly and supportive work environment</li><li>Class 3 Vehicle provided + allowance</li></ul><p><strong>Role Overview:</strong><br />We are looking for a Project Engineer to lead and manage security equipment projects, including installation, testing, commissioning, and system programming, while meeting quality standards.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Lead projects from start to finish, keeping them aligned with objectives</li><li>Coordinate with stakeholders to achieve milestones and meet deadlines</li><li>Act as the main point of contact for clients, ensuring satisfaction and handling escalations</li><li>Deliver projects on time, within budget, and according to agreed specifications</li><li>Manage project teams, assign tasks, and monitor progress</li><li>Maintain proper documentation</li><li>Perform other duties as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Electronics & Communication Engineering or related field</li><li>At least 2 years of relevant experience preferred</li><li>Strong communication and coordination skills</li><li>Highly organized with good time and resource management</li><li>Basic knowledge of ELV, Automation, Networking, and Security Systems (CCTV, Card Access, Alarm Systems) is a plus</li><li>Proactive, problem-solving mindset with a strong sense of initiative</li><li>Experience in the same industry is highly preferred</li></ul><p></p><p>Interested candidates please WhatsApp me at 8779 6100 or send in your resume to willie.goh@swiftsearchglobal.com</p><p><br /></p><p>We regret to inform you that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><br /></p><p>Willie Goh | EA Reg No: R2197853</p><p><br /></p><p>Swift Search Global Pte Ltd | EA No: 18C9495</p><p><br /></p>",
